Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.02,0:23:18.44,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be5}アナタ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.27,0:23:22.50,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be5}互いの殺意で
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.66,0:23:25.49,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be5}トドメ喰らっちゃうね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.39,0:23:30.31,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be5}やっぱりやめとくわ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.30,0:22:19.07,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be5}眼前映入深红一片
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.03,0:22:28.84,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be5}前方约有40000公里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.26,0:22:36.38,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be5}不断逼近彼此的伤痕
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.07,0:22:41.58,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be5}为迷惘前路更添一层迷雾
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.87,0:22:45.97,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be5}摸不找闻不到  无法改变的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.54,0:22:48.33,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be5}直击身后
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.47,0:22:49.51,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be5}所以说
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.64,0:22:57.80,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be5}今夜让我陪在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.27,0:23:07.04,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be5}今晚我是真心实意的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.26,0:23:10.79,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be5}离我再更近一点
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.79,0:23:13.02,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be5}眼见祈愿中的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.02,0:23:15.02,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be5}已经渐行渐远
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.02,0:23:18.44,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be5}亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.27,0:23:22.50,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be5}互相的杀意
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.66,0:23:25.49,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be5}能给对方致命的一击
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.39,0:23:30.31,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be5}还是算了吧
